        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p> <p>Boil a kettle</p> <p>Cut the\u00a0<strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half (chop them<span class=\"text-highlight\"> in</span> one bunch for speed!)</p>",
