        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> gnocchi</strong> and <strong>chopped Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p> <p>Cook\u00a0for 3 min or until the <strong>gnocchi</strong> begins to rise to the top of the pot</p> <p>Once done, drain, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy cooking water</strong></p>",
