        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained gnocchi</strong> and<strong> Tenderstem</strong> to the <strong>creamy sauce</strong>, give everything a good mix up and cook for 1 min or until the sauce begins to stick to the gnocchi</p> <p>Tip: add a small splash of the starchy cooking water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
